title: Listen To This If You Feel Guilt Of Past Mistakes
itunes:author: Joey Kidney
itunes:subtitle: Guilty Number
itunes:summary:
Feeling guilt over something that has happened or something that you have done is normal, but if you have trouble getting past that, then it is time that I think we talk about it. Here are the stages that I think you need to go through to move on.
